| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1321 — Recovery Inhibition (blackbasta)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7d20aec9-1f90-5aa3-8710-44a293368a56"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
